
### Chainsaw ###

Rapidly Search and Hunt through Windows Forensic Artefacts
  -  Chainsaw : https://github.com/WithSecureLabs/chainsaw

Below some commands to use Chainsaw efficiently:
  -  sudo ./chainsaw hunt evtx_attack_samples/ 

We can add SIGMA rules to chainsaw:
  -  sudo ./chainsaw hunt evtx_attack_samples/ --rules sigma_rules/ --mapping mapping_files/sigma-mapping.yml > output2.txt

